{"tid":2444117,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"眼見學生為公義被控 梁晃維中學老師化身送車師：佢盡佢嘅使命感","createTime":"2021-03-12T13:21:55.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-12T13:51:48.000Z","uid":101392,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c10bac4d5b53abe6fb5ab60e88ead1864115528b","tid":2444117,"uid":101392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T13:21:55.000Z","msg":"/梁晃維就讀伊利沙伯中學，其已離職的中學老師林老師，今早8時半已到場排隊旁聽，欲為學生打氣支持，「（我）一路都撐佢㗎」。回憶起與他相處的點滴，林讚揚梁在中學時期乖巧、低調，但對香港充滿熱誠，「未畢業嗰陣已經活躍，喺學生會服務，一路關心香港的發展」。/<br />\n<br />\n/香港司法制度被蓋上「霧霾」，公義難以獲得。林老師嘆整個審訊過程，早已打破了香港整個《普通法》，「所以大家都不必要有任何幻想」。/<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n/看着學生為求爭取公義，未來或需面臨牢獄之苦，林老師坦言：「整體真香港人其實都明白，去到咁嘅情況，（好似）活在戰爭，大家都預咗喺每個角色上盡量付出。」最後亦慨嘆一句，「佢（梁晃維）係做盡咗佢嘅使命感」/<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210312/55HHFFM5NJFLLMIUDQNUEZQ75E/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR2lQC_TloT7qEzcxmRjgC1OXjywCKDFDHbnn0iviRMiuH1tndiUK7OzQ4Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210312%2F55HHFFM5NJFLLMIUDQNUEZQ75E%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR2lQC_TloT7qEzcxmRjgC1OXjywCKDFDHbnn0iviRMiuH1tndiUK7OzQ4Q&d=RYsttnILlo6fxd9QfZlXI0tjIx4W8g%2FGk507jgkcous%3D&h=baeacd70\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210312%2F55HHFFM5NJFLLMIUDQNUEZQ75E%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR2lQC_TloT7qEzcxmRjgC1OXjywCKDFDHbnn0iviRMiuH1tndiUK7OzQ4Q&h=e58b9f60\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210312/55HHFFM5NJFLLMIUDQNUEZQ75E/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR2lQC_TloT7qEzcxmRjgC1OXjywCKDFDHbnn0iviRMiuH1tndiUK7O